                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#" class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove" title="Apagar pessoa"></a>
                </span>
                <span class="thumbnail">
                    <div class="caption">
                        <h4>Prog. PHP</h4>
                        <p>
                            R$40,00 / h<br />
